      *              * stampa                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-tip-ord           =    01
                     go to ril-rec-tst-100
           else if   rr-tip-ord           =    02
                     go to ril-rec-tst-300
           else if   rr-tip-ord           =    03
                     go to ril-rec-tst-400
           else if   rr-tip-ord           =    04
                     go to ril-rec-tst-500.
       ril-rec-tst-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se tipo di ordinamento di stampa 01             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       ril-rec-tst-110.
